AFFIDAVIT OF NON-RECEIPT OF MAINTENANCE ASSESSMENTS
OF CANTERA HILLS HOMEOWNERS ASSOCIATION, INC.
STATE OF TEXAS
COUNTY OF BEXAR
S
"Notice is hereby given that there exists a lien for unpaid maintenance assessments assessed by CANTERA HILLS
HOMEOWNERS ASSOCIATION, INC ., for non-payment by the owner of the subject property and such maintenance assessments
being in accordance with the Cantera Hills, Unit-1 Declaration of Covenants, Conditions, Easements and Restrictions, as
recorded in Volume 18734, Page 583 et seq. in the Official Public Records of Bexar County, Texas; and Certificate of
Annexation and Supplemental Declaration for Cantera Hills, Unit-2, recorded as Document No. 2020035614 in the Official
Public Records of Bexar County, Texas. The property subject to this Affidavit is as follows, to-wit:
SUBJECT PROPERTY:
Address:
Legal Description:
Last Known Owners:
Last Known Address:
Amount of Delinquent:
Assessments and Fees:
23113 Crafty Ridge, San Antonio, Texas 78255
Lot 15, Block 4, CANTERA HILLS, UNIT-2 (ENCLAVE), situated in Bexar
County, Texas, according to plat thereof recorded in Volume 20002, Pages 107-111,
Deed and Plat Records of Bexar County, Texas.
Integrity Homes Inc.
23113 Crafty Ridge, San Antonio, Texas 78255
$2,360.72
Amounts are subject to continued accrual of late fees, interest and collection costs
which shall be automatically added to the lien amount.
Executed this day of APRIL 2022.
By:
Its:
Dallas, Texas 75330
STATE OF TEXAS
COUNTY OF TRAVIS
